<div class=Section1 style='layout-grid:18.0pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><b><span style='font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:
Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:#666666;
mso-font-kerning:0pt'>第七封信</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>你曾傾聽過內心的聲音嗎？</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>「為什麼我們必須傾聽自己的心聲呢？」牧羊少年問道。</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>「因為你的寶藏都在那裡呀！」</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>——</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>摘錄自《牧羊少年奇幻之旅》，保羅</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:新細明體;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;
mso-font-kerning:0pt'>•</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:新細明體;
mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:
新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>科爾賀著</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>「你們這些白人啊，一天到晚問東問西的。你們難道就不能好好觀察和傾聽嗎？人只要懂得觀察和傾聽，大概就能學會所有重要的事情了。」</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>——</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>美國印地安老人之語</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>敬愛的老闆（雖然你依舊保持沉默）：</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>我猜你八成也掉進了「賺錢維生」的陷阱裡了，每天忙著打拚，根本沒時間理我。我想，你天天處理急事，卻錯過了重要的事。</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>突然間，你的沉默卻讓我有了尋找自我的念頭。我找到了，真正的自己其實就藏身在我的沉默裡，那個常讓我感到不安的黑暗角落。</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>有一次，一個好朋友告訴我一句非洲部落的諺語，簡單卻充滿智慧，真實且極具意義，它是這麼說的：「無盡的沉默：震耳的喧嘩。」</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>內心的沉默起初會讓人惶惶不安，因為你突然間會發現，這種沉默其實是虛假的：事實上，你的內心有太多雜音了，這些雜音是一種激烈的表現，有太多不同的聲音、對話和影像不斷地來來去去，困惑、疑難、矛盾交雜叢生</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:
新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>……</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>。看看下面這些例子吧：</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>——</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>「我也很想過得悠閒自在一點啊，可是，誰負責賺錢養家呢？」</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>——</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>「我想多賺點錢讓自己過好一點的日子，但這也意味著我必須更努力工作，自己的時間也變少了，既然這樣，賺那麼多錢給誰花呢？」</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>在這些雜音之間，有個微弱的聲音出現了，像個吱吱作響的小蟋蟀一樣，耐心等待某天會有人聽見它微弱的叫聲。為了避免被雜音干擾，你必須挨近「小蟋蟀」旁，才有可能和它對話。</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>換個方式來說吧：如果你想主導自己的人生，讓生命邁向自己真正想要的目標，首先要做的就是傾聽自己的心聲，時時自我警覺，認真去探究自己到底真正想要的是什麼。</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;
color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'> <span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
line-height:12.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei;
mso-bidi-font-family:新細明體;color:teal;mso-font-kerning:0pt'>自我診斷的第一項工具就是自我傾聽。</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:
新細明體;color:#3366FF;mso-font-kerning:0pt'><a
href="http://www.soho-rich.com/life/"><span style='font-family:新細明體;mso-ascii-font-family:
Taipei;mso-hansi-font-family:Taipei'>讓生命邁向自己真正想要的目標</span></a></span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Taipei;mso-bidi-font-family:
新細明體;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

